Package org.junittest.starwars_server_springconfiguration

Class RegistryForDataFetchersDelegates

java.lang.Object
org.junittest.starwars_server_springconfiguration.RegistryForDataFetchersDelegates
@Component public class RegistryForDataFetchersDelegates extends Object
This registry logs each DataFetchersDelegate spring component. It's used by POJO, when the handle data fetchers members. For instance with this GraphQL type: 
 type Member {
     name(uppercase: Boolean): String
 }
A name(String) data fetcher method is created in the generated Membe POJO. It needs to call the name(String) of the Member DataFetchersDelegate.
Since version 2.5
This class has been renamed as RegistryForDataFetchersDelegates (instead of DataFetchersDelegateRegistry) in 2.9, to avoid name collision with a possible "Registry" type that could be defined in the provided GraphQL schema.
